---
import { SEMINARIO } from '../config/seminario';
---
<section class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200 py-10 md:py-16 px-5">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">

    <p class="text-[11px] md:text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-5">
      Seminário online · gratuito
    </p>

    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 leading-snug tracking-tight">
      Participe do Seminário de Relatórios e descubra exatamente o que colocar no papel — com a técnica certa — nesse momento que vivemos.
    </h1>

    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 mb-6">
      Aula online e gratuita + Certificado de {SEMINARIO.cargaGratuita}
    </p>

    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6 text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-700 mb-1">
      <div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-[10px] md:text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-0.5">Data</p>
        <p class="font-semibold">{SEMINARIO.dataExibida}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-px h-8 bg-gray-200"></div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-[10px] md:text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-0.5">Horário</p>
        <p class="font-semibold">{SEMINARIO.horaExibida}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
